<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٢١٨ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/556">إِسْحَاقُ بْنُ نَصْرٍ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5786">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عُبَيْدٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">عُبَيْدُ اللهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2249">وَسَالِمٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«نَهَى النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> عَنْ أَكْلِ لُحُومِ الْحُمُرِ الْأَهْلِيَّةِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>